@startuml AD_dryrun_current
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Activity Diagram: Datasource Dryrun (Current-State)

|User|
start
:Select datasource and target;
:Trigger dryrun;

|Ingest Service|
:Validate source status and target;
if (Source status allowed?) then (No)
  :Return dryrun not allowed;
  stop
endif

:Create dryrun_result with status RUNNING;
:Mark datasource dryrun status running;
:Publish dryrun dispatch to RabbitMQ;

|Scapper Worker|
:Consume task and fetch sample data;
:Store result and publish dryrun completion;

|Ingest Service|
:Consume completion;
if (Completion success?) then (Yes)
  :Update dryrun_result with samples and status COMPLETED;
  :Update datasource readiness evidence;
else (No)
  :Update dryrun_result with FAILED status;
endif

|User|
:Read latest or history dryrun result;
stop
@enduml
